{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2605755, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "线代确实蛮抽象的", "timestamp": 1632710591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605761, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "线性空间，建立了一个最一般的概念", "timestamp": 1632710642, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605764, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果是应用的话就是矩阵运算和各种处理矩阵的方式？", "timestamp": 1632710666, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605815, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉是通过学习对矩阵的处理方法，来处理大规模的线性运算。一个典型的应用是利用各种矩阵的分解求解线性方程组。当然前几节课还是基础的概念和运算法则，以及建立线性空间的概念。", "timestamp": 1632711233, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605818, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "讲的是怎么解大规模的线性方程组的问题（逃）", "timestamp": 1632711248, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605844, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一切数学都是线性代数（确信", "timestamp": 1632711568, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605857, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "多刷题？", "timestamp": 1632711721, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2605885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同Bob，看你学线性代数的目的和院系了", "timestamp": 1632712014, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2606175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 497328, "reply_to": 2605761, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 感觉线性代数一开始都在证很多很显然的东西，这部分很重要吗？", "timestamp": 163271